title: Plonk - Season 1 Complete PDTV.XviD-NoGrp
description: The web-to-TV series Plonk is about an inept trio of TV-makers trying to make a show about the wine industry; think Frontline crossed with The Larry Sanders Show, with Chaser alumni Chris Taylor in the role of the conceited, self-involved presenter, Joshua Tyler as his slightly idiotic sidekick and gopher, and Nathan Earl as the pragmatic producer cleaning up the mess they leave in their wake
